Name  get_metric_definition  -  Returns the metric definition of the specified
       metric
Syntax
Parameters -help Outputs a brief description that includes  type  and  default
       information  for  each  get_metric_definition parameter. For a detailed
       description of the command and all of its parameters, use the man  com-
       mand:  man get_metric_definition -id <metric_id> Specifies the database
       ID to output. Data_type: string, optional -name <label_name>  Specifies
       the metric name. Data_type: string, required
